WEBVTT

00:03:28.812 --> 00:03:31.552
On je kod kuće s moje dvoje dece,

00:03:31.576 --> 00:03:34.266
a još jedno mi raste ovde.

00:03:34.869 --> 00:03:40.044
(Aplauz)

00:03:40.594 --> 00:03:43.939
Kad radim, zovem ga na svaka dva sata

00:03:43.963 --> 00:03:47.753
i on zna da, ako mu se ne javim,

00:03:47.777 --> 00:03:49.204
mora da nazove kontakt osobu,

00:03:49.228 --> 00:03:52.390
onoga ko mi je dao pristup priči,

00:03:52.414 --> 00:03:55.004
a to je osoba od poverenja.

00:03:57.105 --> 00:03:59.130
Jedanput u Gazi,

00:03:59.154 --> 00:04:04.093
tokom otmice
britanskog novinara Alana Džonstona,